# Consumer .npmrc for installing @low-orbit-studio/visor-themes-private
#
# This file scopes only the @low-orbit-studio package namespace to GitHub Packages
# and provides the auth token via the GITHUB_PACKAGES_TOKEN environment variable.
#
# The PAT must belong to a user with read access to the
# `low-orbit-studio/visor-themes-private` repo (read:packages scope, fine-grained).
#
# When GITHUB_PACKAGES_TOKEN is unset, npm install of @low-orbit-studio/visor-themes-private
# will fail authentication. Because the package is listed as an optional dependency,
# npm install continues; the docs build then renders /themes/private as 404.

@low-orbit-studio:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${GITHUB_PACKAGES_TOKEN}
